      append to execution_order, remove from unscheduled.
      Remove each job from eligible immediately after it is scheduled.
   4. ADVANCE: if no job was scheduled in step 3 and unscheduled jobs remain,
      advance current_time = min(end_time for all jobs in active_jobs).
